== About me
I received the B.Eng. in electronic engineering from the [https://www.uestc.edu.cn Univeristy of Electronic Science and Techonology of China (UESTC)], Chengdu, China, in 2017, and Ph.D. degree in computer and information engineering from [https://www.cuhk.edu.cn The Chinese University of Hong Kong, Shenzhen (CUHK-SZ)], China, in 2023, under the supervision of [https://myweb.cuhk.edu.cn/huangchuan Prof. Chuan Huang]. I was a visiting student with the Shenzhen Research Institute of Big Data, Shenzhen, and Purple Mountain Laboratories, Nanjing. Currently, I am a Postdoctoral Fellow with the Department of Electronic and Computer Engineering, [https://www.hkust.edu.hk/en Hong Kong University of Science and Engineering (HKUST)], under the supervision of [https://eekhaled.home.ece.ust.hk Prof. Khaled B. Letaief] and [https://eejzhang.people.ust.hk Prof. Jun Zhang]. 


